---

<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>📬 Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>I'm always open to discussing new projects, creative ideas, or opportunities to be part of your vision.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card glass-card">
      <div class="contact-primary">
        <div class="email-display">codewithnaman@outlook.com</div>
        <div class="contact-meta">
          <span class="location-badge">📍 Pune, India</span>
          <span class="status-badge"><span class="pulse-dot"></span> Open to opportunities</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:codewithnaman@outlook.com" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-purple); }
  .contact-card { padding: 2.5rem; text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .contact-primary { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .email-display {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-green), var(--accent-purple));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .contact-meta { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .location-badge { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9375rem; }
  .status-badge { color: var(--accent-green); font-size: 0.9375rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .pulse-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-green);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.2); }
  }
  .btn-primary { display: inline-flex; width: 100%; justify-content: center; padding: 1rem; font-size: 1rem; }
</style>